{"tid":1397940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁多位如果真係罷唔到工 都仲有方法出力","createTime":"2019-08-02T15:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:15:06.000Z","uid":200230,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2648210b3e09e2b16f17a617aca78a19db68ea5","tid":1397940,"uid":200230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"明白有啲人有唔同原因而5/8罷唔到工，例如醫護界嘅朋友一罷工好多人嘅醫治會受耽誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係你地又可能想出一分力? 咁你地可以將嗰日嘅人工攞去買物資畀義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者捐一日糧畀反送中啲機構，例如星火，幫義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係但係記住唔好當捐份糧就係贖罪券，你有能力罷嘅就一定要罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b08940d7072079f32ec8cad6008559a947ee2865","tid":1397940,"uid":200230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"推上熱門畀多啲人睇到 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2756b7ae2259687d2809c8083fd2f424cab39c","tid":1397940,"uid":200230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d09acfa689bcc2812d0784d9ed92b3786461221","tid":1397940,"uid":296789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n打算果日做連儂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34805e91a92f8b2c448cb383a7d0ead6ffdf04d4","tid":1397940,"uid":200230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d09acfa689bcc2812d0784d9ed92b3786461221","tid":1397940,"uid":296789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n打算果日做連儂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"reply